  "body": "I wish to question [this line](https://github.com/prometheus/prometheus/blob/master/discovery/dns/dns.go#L185). It is commented:\r\n\r\n> // Remove the final dot from rooted DNS names to make them look more usual.\r\n\r\nbut why do we care how it _looks_?  A rooted name has a different meaning from a non-rooted name.\r\n\r\nMore practically, in a typical Kubernetes installation it causes 4-5 pointless DNS lookups as the search path is traversed.",
